IdentityCheckTimeout

Description:  Determines the timeout duration for ident requests 
Syntax:   IdentityCheckTimeout  seconds   
Default:   IdentityCheckTimeout 30  
Context:  server config, virtual host, directory 
Status:  Extension 
Module:  mod_ident 

 This directive specifies the timeout duration of an ident
    request. The default value of 30 seconds is recommended by  RFC 1413 , mainly because
    of possible network latency. However, you may want to adjust the
    timeout value according to your local network speed. 

 